Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利艦隊接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將進入射程範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我名聲掃地的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要成為我高昇的墊腳石
