Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 殲滅海賊一事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可謂功勳彪炳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 下去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關亞瑟斯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚弟他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他保持聯繫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們關係親密 有些矛盾很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要讓你的母親傷心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為人子 都不願看到母親的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯的事情已經傳入殿下耳中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞這些幼稚的把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人 孩兒回來了
