Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親她有這麼輕嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人 孩兒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去喝杯茶如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
