Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1035,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用通訊線路直接說比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(771,983)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國 第二公主莉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(771,913)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞的真假如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 看來方修利確實有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然以人質要脅 身為泰坦尼亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主 法爾密很會寫信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是雪中送炭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 法爾 接下來就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶大佐為了急轉直下的情況不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一動也不動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利艦隊已經停多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就要滿一小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我們繼續和對方大眼瞪小眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過那種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 這才是他的意圖所在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在誘使我們焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我們失去理智 步調紊亂的時候發起總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利 擅長心理戰的不只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊是艾曼塔的空港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於突然封港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨船船員們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你們管事的出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 要你叫你們老大出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}米哈伊爾·瓦倫科夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミハエル・ワレンコフ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊已經出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1164,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1164,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的腦袋真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要交給李博士就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(521,863)\fad(500,500)}米蘭達·卡西米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(521,933)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃個便飯罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入國手續都辦妥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1238,923)\fad(500,500)}路易·艾德蒙·巴傑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1238,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ルイ・エドモン・パジェス
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經辦妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然當場對全員來個搜身檢查？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是索尼婭少佐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}索尼婭少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ソニア少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽李說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們願助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妳這句話我們就放心了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 妳們認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾曼塔有數個反泰坦尼亞的地下組織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們卡薩比安卡公國那種小派
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到她這種大幫都有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐 您從軍過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李博士說空手來就行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就什麼都沒準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我不喜歡虛情假意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 他還好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是亞瑟斯·泰坦尼亞的官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍被森林環繞著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來悠然自得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上戒備森嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利 你想必知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我來說明作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還真是閒啊 伯爵閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴·鮑爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}佛羅利蒙德·戴·鮑爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}フロリモンド・デ・ボーア
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受命擔任警衛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你害死了奶奶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾說過你看錯我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話 我原封不動地還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我只是從夢中醒來了罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 攻進敵陣無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但方修利要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下官知道 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我要進行作戰準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你旗開得勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶 真是個討厭的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到方修利以後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿來做牠們的飼料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.05,0:12:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利艦隊 進入映像通信圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出即時影像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被小看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來 敵人只有方修利的船艦罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我接亞瑟斯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來重獲自由了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 偏偏在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准放任何人進來！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 貝魯提耶大佐來電
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也不太妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 方修利那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說方修利？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫我 我也奈何不了這扇門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉小姐在三樓的客房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵不知道你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大鬧正門將警衛引過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵就易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 我們在這裡阻擋敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.49,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴·鮑爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的軍服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個笨蛋背叛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來莉拉獨力逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪兒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不要再放手了 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐 泰坦尼亞的增援部隊即將趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我號令 全軍撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點 方修利的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼方修利的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准隨便稱呼我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下趕我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到妳沒事 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶… 奶奶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢算計我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你終於記住我的名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你還有點腦子嘛 伯爵閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人負責迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看牠好像餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家孩子們比較喜歡女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要帶我去什麼地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去天城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不准碰莉拉一根指頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就隨你處置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像還不清楚情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩是死是活已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要和我一起去天城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有選擇的餘地 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是希望所在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能把你交給泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見你最後一面 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉 我馬上去救妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方 受不了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 緊急攀升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是米蘭達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 莉拉 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明才要開始的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.53,0:20:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多想說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些 那些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏡子… 鏡子在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}亞瑟斯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是我的錯覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以隕石為掩護平安逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下在追查亞瑟斯伯爵的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發現 就會通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙… 一定要由我親手…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉·佛羅倫茲的死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.27,0:22:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督首次燃起了對泰坦尼亞的仇恨怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.25,0:24:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那完美無瑕的臉龐…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.43,0:24:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩兒為什麼要受到這種待遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.21,0:24:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(647,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}結束與開始


